io.github.rubenchristoffer.hetty.html

Class HTMLNodeWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.rubenchristoffer.hetty.html.HTMLNodeWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<HTMLNodeWrapper>, Node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HTMLDocumentWrapper

    public class HTMLNodeWrapper
extends Object
implements Node, Iterable<HTMLNodeWrapper>
    Wrapper class for HTML DOM Node. Allows for iteration (in a for-each loop or using iterator) Also has a few helper functions.
    Author:
    Ruben Christoffer

        Same as getNodeListWrapperByName(String), but only adds node to list if it fulfills all the predicates passed.
        Parameters:
        name - is the name of the node(s)
        predicates - is all the predicates that each node has to pass to be added to list

        wrapped node list containing nodes with name that have passed all predicates
